---
title: Quick Beef Rissoles with Herby Crouton & Crumbly Cheese Salad
description: These simple rustic rissoles are packed with moisture and flavour from spinach and slightly salty crumbly cheese. They’re the
perfect little parcels of joy to be savoured with a simple Greek-style crouton salad and a herbed mayonnaise.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spinach-feta-rissoles-c40f3b3e.jpg
